:: Q1-3 {"position":"1625,1625","size":"100,100"}
You approach the farmer with the farming equipment. 

FARMER: Thanks Ash, I owe you one. Actually here, take this (+200 Gold) (set:$Gold to it + 200). Now we're even. Oh, actually let me tell you a rumor that might interest you. Apparently, each of Oak's starter pokemon can do something special in route 1. Might be worth checking out.

QUEST #1 COMPLETE (set:$Qindex's Q1 to "Complete")

[[Back->PalletField]]


:: Quests {"position":"350,50","size":"100,100"}
<img src="Images\PokyDex.png"> : Along the way, you'll find many NPCs who can give you quests. Some of them are long and epic, some of them are short and basic. There's a "main quest" of sorts, but you probably won't stay on the main path for long with the amount of side content there is.

[[Back->New Game]]


:: R1-1Passage {"position":"1400,1175","size":"100,100"}
Charmander uses his flames to burn a way through the bush. You can now clearly see the passage, and a light at the end of it. You head through. The passage is tight, but you manage to get to the bigger lit cavern at the end of it. Blue mushrooms are making the light, which gives a calming tone to the whole cave. In the center, you see a rock pillar. On it is a satchel with 50 Pokeballs! You exit the cave.
(set:$R1CaveFound to 1)(set:$PokeballCount to it + 50)
[[Back->Route 1-1]]


:: R1-2Pond {"position":"1400,1050","size":"100,100"}
Squirtle dives into the lake, and swims its way to the bottom. You see it grab the item you spotted. It heads back to the surface. You notice that the blue skin is actually great camouflage in water. Squirtle gives you the item it found. It's a satchel containing 25 potions! You head back to the main path.
(set:$R1PondFound to 1)(set:$PotionCount to it + 25)
[[Back->Route 1-2]]


:: R1-3Butter {"position":"1400,925","size":"100,100"}
Bulbasaur uses his incredibly fast vines to grab the item straight from Butterfree's... hands? Bulbasaur gives you the item. It's a satchel, containing a Pokedex Decoration! It would look good in your room. You head back to the main path, not questioning how this Butterfree conveniently got a satchel with a decoration in it.
(set:$R1ButterfreeFound to 1)(set:$Inventory to it + (a:"Pokedex Decoration"))
[[Back->Route 1-3]]


