:: Route 1-1 {"position":"1300,1175","size":"100,100"}
ROUTE 1

You're walking along Route 1. You can see Pallet Town in the valley below. In front of you are several thick bushes. One of them seems to be blocking the entrance to a small passage on the side of the road. You let (print:$Party's 1's Species) out to walk with you, and it's walking alongside you. There is a sign here.

(print:$Party's 1's png) : (print:$PKindex's ($Party's 1's Species)'s Cry)

[[Read Sign->R1Sign]]
(link:"North")[(set:$Return to "Route 1-2")(go-to:"RouteEncounter")]
[[South->PalletCenter]]
(if: (find: _mon where _mon's Species is "Charmander", ...$Party)'s length > 0 and $R1CaveFound is 0)[[[(Charmander) Burn the bush blocking the passage->R1-1Passage]]<br>]
[[Menu]]

(set:$Location to "Route 1-1")
(set:$EncounterTable to $Route1Table)


:: Route 1-2 {"position":"1300,1050","size":"100,100"}
ROUTE 1

You're walking along Route 1. You're at the middle point of the path. Looking around you, you see a lake. Looks like something is at the bottom of it. Too deep for your arm to reach though, and you don't want to get wet. You let (print:$Party's 1's Species) out to walk with you, and it's walking alongside you. There is a sign here.

(print:$Party's 1's png) : (print:$PKindex's ($Party's 1's Species)'s Cry)

[[Read Sign->R1Sign]]
(link:"North")[(set:$Return to "Route 1-3")(go-to:"RouteEncounter")]
(link:"South")[(set:$Return to "Route 1-1")(go-to:"RouteEncounter")]
(if: (find: _mon where _mon's Species is "Squirtle", ...$Party)'s length > 0 and $R1PondFound is 0)[[[(Squirtle) Make it dive to the bottom->R1-2Pond]]<br>]
[[Menu]]

(set:$Location to "Route 1-2")
(set:$EncounterTable to $Route1Table)


:: Route 1-3 {"position":"1300,925","size":"100,100"}
ROUTE 1

You're walking along Route 1. You can see the tall buildings of Viridian City from here. Looking around you, you see some butterfrees flying around. One of them is holding something. They're too quick for you to catch them. You let (print:$Party's 1's Species) out to walk with you, and it's walking alongside you. There is a sign here.

(print:$Party's 1's png) : (print:$PKindex's ($Party's 1's Species)'s Cry)

[[Read Sign->R1Sign]]
[[North->ViridianEntry]]
(link:"South")[(set:$Return to "Route 1-2")(go-to:"RouteEncounter")]
(if: (find: _mon where _mon's Species is "Bulbasaur", ...$Party)'s length > 0 and $R1ButterfreeFound is 0)[[[(Bulbasaur) Make it grab the item with its vines->R1-3Butter]]<br>]
[[Menu]]

(set:$Location to "Route 1-3")
(set:$EncounterTable to $Route1Table)


:: RouteEncounter {"position":"1700,1100","size":"100,100"}
(if:(random:100)<50)[
	(set: _roll to (random:1,100))
    (set: _total to 0)
    
    (for: each _entry, ...$EncounterTable)[
    	(set: _total to _total + _entry's Rate)
        
        (if: _roll <= _total)[
        	(set:$EnemySpecies to _entry's Species)
            (set:$EnemyLevel to (random: _entry's min, _entry's max))
            (go-to:"BattleIntro")
        ]
	]
        

](else:)[(go-to:$Return)]


