:: The Field {"position":"350,150","size":"100,100"}
<img src="Images\PokyDex.png"> : As a Pokemon trainer, you'll spend most of your time in the fields. This game doesn't just have basic roads. You can delve into mini dungeons, do special random events, catch pokemon of course, and more! It's a huge world out there, I hope you'll be able to see all of it!

